column12: Measurement condition : Clear; Clear , No Precipitation , Calm Wind
column14: Q was manually calculated by timed ice pans and a historical mmnt for area. The distance used to calculate the times ice pans was both written down wrong and then calculated wrong. See revised M1 PDF.  The velocity was unlike any other velocity at this stage and it was pressumed to be taken over 20 m and not 10 or 40m.. the original calculation showed 1.0m/s but it was actually 2.0m/s and faster than walking speed which is 1.5m/s.  It totally fits on the discharge hydrograph now and does not need to be thrown out.  CM Dec 08, 2023.
